{"tid":1278180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「至高登巴打」對呢到有人屈人地同香討同路，我向各位巴打道歉！","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:48:39.000Z","uid":12628,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66831d7a76f6e5f9a471d5c7417e30a8750dec7d","tid":1278180,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"大事大非面前，不分化，不割席！<br />\n高登巴打係呢場運動入面，好多出心出力，有啲過左黎背後冊劃每次行動，用佢地嘅經驗分享，幫後生一輩有效率抗爭，避免重滔覆轍！<br />\n呢啲有部分小朋友！玩膠玩到離晒譜！<br />\n屈高登巴打同香討，baby condom同級，<br />\n我唔否認高登有5毛，熱狗搞事，<br />\n不過呢啲野，連登一樣有！<br />\n高登嘅巴絲大至上同連登嘅大多數巴絲一樣，<br />\n為今場運動流淚流血！<br />\n出面分化高登班撚樣，我祝晒你地長命百歲，百病纏身！<br />\n高登各巴絲，我向你地真誠道歉！<br />\n希望大家唔好比啲小人分化！<br />\n著眼返我地共同嘅目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f938d0b51945a0f61fdd34d95ea6579f0ad31767","tid":1278180,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4143/4795282150_9bde0b434a_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F4143%2F4795282150_9bde0b434a_z.jpg&h=00f2acab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ibook.idv.tw/wmv/movie/movie48/edmm1431_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fibook.idv.tw%2Fwmv%2Fmovie%2Fmovie48%2Fedmm1431_1.jpg&h=0e937511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tmlKy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtmlKy.jpg&h=bc34545c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b687a058f717175e057c4ed413b6d15e7fb62a0b","tid":1278180,"uid":162978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:26:17.000Z","msg":"一個名幾錢"},{"pid":"4f7d1fddb7eefead936c1eb0519cfaaa6ce30668","tid":1278180,"uid":162978,"like":0,"dislike"